-- Iraq Signs Deal to Construct First Drilling Fluids Plant
-- B y   K h a l i d   A l - A n s a r y
-- 2012-08-08T10:35:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-08/iraq-signs-deal-to-construct-first-drilling-fluids-plant.html
Iraq  signed contracts with Oren
Hydrocarbons Middle East Inc. for the construction of the
country’s first drilling fluids plant, the director general of
Iraq’s Free Zones Committee said.  The facility will be built in Khor al-Zubair in southern
Iraq, Sabah al-Qaisi said by phone from Baghdad today.  To contact the reporters on this story:
